The tech stack for this project includes:

Languages: TypeScript (primarily), JavaScript (for specific cases like configuration, third-party libraries, or legacy code), CSS, HTML, SQL
Frontend: React, Vite, Tailwind CSS, Radix UI, Framer Motion, Lucide React, Recharts
Backend: Express.js, Supabase
Other Libraries: Axios, Zod, OpenAI, class-variance-authority, clsx, tailwind-merge, etc.
Package Manager: pnpm
Coding Rule: Prefer .ts files for all new code. Use .js files only when necessary for configuration, third-party libraries without type definitions, or legacy code.